OL,3,CPickup truck crashes into house in
OL,4,CDerrylin
OL,6,FA man has been arrested and "extensive
OL,7,Fdamage" caused after a pickup truck
OL,8,Fcrashed into a house in Co Fermanagh.
OL,10,FPolice said the crash, involving a
OL,11,Fdark grey Toyota Hilux, happened in
OL,12,Fthe Ballyconnell Road area of Derrylin
OL,13,Fon Sunday night.
OL,15,FOfficers were called to the scene,
OL,16,Falongside members of the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Fire and Rescue Service, and
OL,18,Ffound the occupants of the vehicle had
OL,19,F"made off".
