OL,3,CPickup truck crashes into house in
OL,4,CDerrylin
OL,6,FA 19-year-old man was arrested a short
OL,7,Ftime later on suspicion of driving
OL,8,Fwhile intoxicated, failing to stop,
OL,9,Fremain and report, and dangerous
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FHe has since been released on bail.
